name: Deposit
description:
I require a $25 deposit for ANY & ALL appointments. 
Please leave your contact info and the best way to reach you in the notes at checkout. I will then contact you to confirm your appointment. 

OPTIONAL: You may email me BEFORE you book an appointment to schedule your Skype or FaceTime consult via email strandzofbeauty@gmail.com

Late fees: I charge a $25 late after 15mins do being late, after 30 mins your appointment has been cancelled. 
If you are going to be late (call/text me to reschedule)
No call No show means I am no longer your stylist. Deposit is no refundable. I love all you guys, but time is VALUABLE.
I DO NOT overbook, your time is your time. If you do not respect my time I will be unable to service you

Cancellations: If you need to cancel your appointment, please do so within in 24hours of your appointment. (I know life happens & I am understanding) You may then reschedule your appointment with me

name: Brazilian
description: Brazilian Hair is the most sought after texture on the market right now. This hair is used diversely because of its softness, durability and density (thickness). This texture is easiest to blend with most ethnicities from some Caucasian textures to African American relaxed textures. Brazilian hair is extremely luxurious and very soft with a lot of body and natural shine. Its luster is low to medium. This hair very versatile!

name: Indian
description:
It's the most versatile and readily available on the market. The hairs density is very fine. It's naturally airy, light and bouncy and can easily be curled and styled. Indian hair moves effortlessly with minimal products. It also blends well with most hair textures. This hair texture can be found ranging from silky to lightly coarse.

This hair will swell and become frizzy in humid weather and in foggy conditions. Anti-frizz products are highly suggested.

name: Malaysian
description: Malaysian Hair is a highly sought after texture and a very popular option among celebrities. Malaysian hair has an extremely luxurious feel and is sleek and shiny, but not excessively shiny. Its luster is low to medium-similar to Brazilian hair. This hair hold curls extremely well without the use of products. It  is generally very dark brown; close to black with some bundles may having lighter ends. This hair blends very well with most hair types including African American. It does not swell or frizz in humid conditions making it low maintenance. This hair is PHENOMENAL!!!

name: Peruvian
description: Peruvian Hair is the ultimate multi-purpose hair! It's extremely soft and ultimately feather light! You can have up to five bundles of a Peruvian hair installed yet still maintain a feathery light, maintainable style. This hair is coarser in texture than Indian or Brazilian hair and its luster is low to medium. It blends very well with African-American relaxed hair textures and medium Caucasian hair textures. This hair is Luxurious

name: European
description: European Hair is naturally straight, it is ideal for the client who wants pin straight hair and can create a great blend. European hair will remain fairly straight (even after shampooing), it can be curled,but the texture of our hair is meant to remain with it natural state "STRAIGHT".

name: Cambodian
description: Cambodian hair is light, silky and lustrous in texture which is one of the reasons that it's the most popular type of hair extensions in the market. The light texture of the Cambodian human hair makes it effortless to wear and maintain. With proper care, Cambodian human hair will not mat or tangle and maintain its silky, luscious state.

name: Mongolian
description: Mongolian hair is one of our highest (AAAAA) grade(s) of hair, preferred by most women who like to vary in Hair styles. It has a natural healthy sheen a little extra body, tangle and frizz-free! Don't we love our tangle free! Mongolian Hair is as natural as your own hair, it holds curls really well, but the texture of our hair is meant to remain with straight and/or body wave. Mongolian hair can be blended into hair of all ethnicities. Like all of our hair (Brazilian, Peruvian, Indian,etc), it can be used more than once and at least 6+ months with professional care.

name: Closures
description: Our Front Closures will give you a natural looking weave, without leaving any of your natural hair out. The lace under the closure will allow you to part and style the hair, all while having a natural looking scalp. Closures are especially great for those who have unmanageable hair, or to protect your leave out from heat damage.
